				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Odd occurence the other day with Defense skill ups<a name="75509"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 17 05 3:33 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Thursday moring, after Tuesday patch I was in a group in WoS Murk caves.  Not anything crazy, just grinding to 69 when I started noticing defense skill ups.  Now,  I have been stuck at 246 forever. 
<br />
 Well, it seems I have had a total of maybe, MAYBE 5 skill ups in all of 67 and 68.
<br />

<br />
What caught my eye was this, I was getting upwards of 5 defense skill ups on a pull of 1 mob!  
<br />

<br />
In 2.5 hours, I went from 246 defense to 266!  
<br />
20 skill up points in 2.5 hours!!!
<br />
Shocked was an understatement, I was calling it out in group and they finally said there was no way anyone could get that may defense skill ups in that legnth of time.
<br />

<br />
I talked about it over GC and someone said that the patch that changed the trade-skills patch may have had something to do with my defense skill up run.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Anyone else see anything like this or an I just EXTREMELY lucky??
<br />

<br />
BTW, this is the greatest bard site I have ever been to and this site alone has helped me become a better bard<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Melodymaker
<br />
The Tribunal
<br />
Mithril Heart Brigade</span></td>
