				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Odd occurence the other day with Defense skill ups<a name="76052"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 2 05 12:48 PM</span></td>
