				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Have you done this yourself Treeb, or have you only heard about it? </span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
I've done it myself.  Recently.  I leveled from 65 to 66 about 3 weeks ago (or so) and re-capped my defense skillups on a swarm of Hobgoblins/Nettling Wraiths in PoN.  IIRC, it took me probably between 4 to 6 cycles of DA before I re-capped my defense for level 66.
<br />

<br />
Recommendation:  Don't forget the AGI buffs.  Grab and AGI Buff from a friendly neighborhood Shammy and also pulse Nillipuss (lvl 52 song) right before you activate DA/Deftdance.
<br />

<br />
Do the above and try it again.  You may have just had some bad RNG results that day.  I'd give it another shot if I were you.  I've done the same every time I've leveled since level 57.  It'll work, just buff your AGI up and try again.
<br />

<br />
EDIT:  Oops, sorry, I just saw that you said you <b>did</b> get your AGI buffed up.  Still though, I'd give it another shot.  It's worked <b>GREAT</b> for me.
<br />

