				<td colspan="2"><span>I only use the DA song, but it still scares me when I do it.  I always keep my cursor on my icons and when it says 0:00, I count to 4 then run out.  Normally that gives me about 1 sec window before song drops.  Little tip for people using the song to raise defense skills.  It seems like the timer on the song refreshes faster when you go zone out and zone back in.  Then by the time you have all your mobs gathered back up, the song is good to go.  Maybe it doesn't actually help, but it sure seems to go faster than just sitting and waiting.</span></td>
